Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine a student from a remote part of J&K and Ladakh, full of hope, applying for a scholarship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that would change their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of focusing on the studies, they are caught in a frustrating cycle, printing documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,traveling to verification centers and waiting for approvals that seem to take forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The process is slow, confusing and full of paperwork, often leading to delays that leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,students in a limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just the students facing the challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side, the FC center is overwhelmed with the task of manually verifying thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of documents from the applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine an alternative, a system where students can apply for their scholarships from the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The workflow documents digitally and track their application status in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No paperwork, no long wait times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The SHE Bureau, too benefit from the automated verification and streamlined workflows enabling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,them to review applications faster and with greater accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what we, Team CODENITI, aim to achieve with our paperless scholarship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,disbursement system for the Prime Minister's special scholarships scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jheel Jain and along with my team we have built a system that eliminates the need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for manual verification by leveraging technologies like optical character recognition and DigiLocker for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,secure document authentication.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Students can upload the documents directly while the SHE Bureau can automate verification
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and focus on critical cases by reducing manual steps via ensuring faster, more transparent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and reliable scholarship disbursement.
